'''脉冲'''（{{lang-en|Pulse}}）是位于美国[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[奥兰多|奥兰多]]的一家同性恋舞厅酒吧，于2004年由芭芭拉·波马和罗恩·雷格勒创立。2016年6月12日，夜店因是造成49人死，53人伤的美国历史上[[2016年奥兰多夜店枪击案|由单个枪手引发的死伤最严重大规模枪击案]]和自[[九一一恐怖袭击|九一一恐怖袭击]]以来美国本土最致命的恐怖袭击现场，而受到国际社会的关注。

== 简介 ==
[[File:Procession_of_Pulse_nightclub_at_Come_Out_With_Pride_Parade_2009_(4010590470).jpg|thumb]]

脉冲每晚都会举行主题演出，每月有面向[[同性恋社群|同性恋社群]]的教育活动<ref name=Hjelmgaard>{{Cite news |url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2016/06/12/pulse-more-than-just-another-gay-club/85785762/ |title = Scene of mass shooting more than 'just another gay club' |work = USA Today |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |first = Kim |last = Hjelmgaard |date = 2016-06-12 |issn = 0734-7456 |publisher = Gannett Company |archive-date = 2021-03-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210303015033/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2016/06/12/pulse-more-than-just-another-gay-club/85785762/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。根据《奥兰多周刊》，脉冲设有三个“眩目、震动的房间，让俱乐部男孩、{{le|年轻男同性恋|Twink (gay slang)}}之间零距离接触”。尽管每晚出售的东西都不一样，但脉冲最有名的是令人印象深刻的[[男扮女装|男扮女装]]表演，酒店舞者通常很华丽<ref>{{cite news |title = Orlando gay bars |url = http://www.orlandoweekly.com/orlando/orlando-gay-bars/Content?oid=2244768 |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |work = Orlando Weekly |publisher = Euclid Media Group |archive-date = 2021-01-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210115153927/https://www.orlandoweekly.com/orlando/orlando-gay-bars/Content?oid=2244768 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。基于这三个方面，《[[孤独星球|孤独星球]]探索佛罗里达》（{{lang|en|''Lonely Planet Discover Florida''}}）认为它是“三个夜店的合体”<ref name="PlanetKarlin2012">{{cite book|author1=Adam Karlin|author2=Jeff Campbell|author3=Jennifer Rasin Denniston|author4=Emily Matchar|title=Lonely Planet Discover Florida|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=JhD_e1z9dPMC&pg=PT154|date=June 1, 2012|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74321-015-4|page=154}}</ref>，而该社的《佛罗里达》卷则侧重介绍它的“超现代化”<ref name="PlanetKarlin2014">{{cite book|author1=Adam Karlin|author2=Jennifer Rasin Denniston|author3=Paula Hardy|author4=Benedict Walker|title=Lonely Planet Florida|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=reXUBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT615|date=2014-12-01|publisher=Lonely Planet Publications|isbn=978-1-74360-250-8|page=615}}</ref>。

《奥兰多十宗最》（{{lang|en|''Top 10 Orlando''}}）称它是“奥兰多同性恋群体最喜欢的场所”<ref name="TunstallTunstall2012">{{cite book|author1=Cynthia Tunstall|author2=Jim Tunstall|title=Top 10 Orlando|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=wFmzDyga48AC&pg=PA79|date=August 1, 2012|publisher=DK Publishing|isbn=978-0-7566-9461-6|page=79}}</ref>。《佛罗里达州{{le|简明指南|Rough Guides}}》表示它“无可厚非地受欢迎”，强调其“出众的灯光音响、歌舞表演、男扮女装行为和色情舞者”<ref name="Guides2009">{{cite book|author=Rough Guides|title=The Rough Guide to Florida|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=XNJaAomoSGwC&pg=PT319|accessdate=June 13, 2016|edition=8th|date=August 3, 2009|publisher=Penguin Group|isbn=978-1-4053-8013-3|page=319}}</ref>。《美国简明指南》（{{lang|en|''The Rough Guide to the USA''}}）指出脉冲是奥兰多唯一一间同性恋酒吧<ref name="Cook2011">{{cite book|author=Samantha Cook|title=The Rough Guide to the USA|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=E1qZJLwDlTUC&pg=PT1082|date=2011-03-01|publisher=Rough Guides|isbn=978-1-4053-8954-9|page=1082}}</ref>。各大列表显示，包括洗手间在内的整个场所都可以使用<ref name="Green2012">{{cite book|author=Frances Green|title=Gayellow Pages USA #34 2012-2013|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=e1SIUkQupUYC&pg=PA276|date=2012-04-01|publisher=Renaissance House|isbn=978-1-885404-28-2|page=276}}</ref>。{{le|Zagat|Zagat}}借助“定期消费者调查”，给脉冲的气氛、装潢和服务各打25分、25分和22分（满分30）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.zagat.com/n/pulse-orlando|title=PULSE - Zagat Review|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-13}}</ref>。游客可以每天早上 7 点 30 分开始参观这里的夜店。直到凌晨 12:00。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://zaubee.com/biz/pulse-7qwn2px1 |title=Pulse nightclub |website=|language=en|access-date=2022-06-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220624062740/https://zaubee.com/biz/pulse-7qwn2px1 |archivedate=June 24, 2022}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
[[File:President_Obama_Delivers_a_Statement_in_Orlando.webm|thumb]]

脉冲成立前，南奥兰治大道1912号是20世纪30年代日报社萨拉索塔先驱报公司（{{lang|en|Sarasota Herald Company}}）的所在地<ref>{{cite news|title=Sarasota Herald|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&dat=19360205&id=SjoeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1L4EAAAAIBAJ&pg=1912,2664730&hl=en|accessdate=2016-06-13|work=Sarasota Herald-Tribune|date=1936-02-05|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306141158/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1755&dat=19360205&id=SjoeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1L4EAAAAIBAJ&pg=1912,2664730&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1985年，这里开了一家名为洛伦佐（{{lang|en|Lorenzo's}}）的比萨饼店<ref>{{cite web |url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com.dclibrary.idm.oclc.org/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=0EB6BE85DBC12128&p_docnum=1&p_queryname=12 |title=What's Cooking in Pizza Circles |author=Chris Sherman |website=''The Orlando Sentinel'' |date=1985-07-19}}</ref>。到1999年，这里有现场音乐表演酒吧但丁（{{lang|en|Dante's}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com.dclibrary.idm.oclc.org/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=0EB4F4B5FA0CC687&p_docnum=5&p_queryname=12 |title=A Fortuitous Fusion |author=Scott Joseph |website=''The Orlando Sentinel'' |date=1999-02-26}}</ref>。2003年1月，但丁倒闭<ref>{{cite web |url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com.dclibrary.idm.oclc.org/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=0F8A03E74AFA8320&p_docnum=48&p_queryname=12 |title=Caught in Headlightz: Bar Changes Act|author=Tyler Gray |website=''The Orlando Sentinel'' |date=2003-01-17}}</ref>。

夜店于2004年7月2日由芭芭拉·波马和罗恩·雷格勒创立<ref name=open>{{cite web |url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com.dclibrary.idm.oclc.org/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=103BA6AFE9AF4C05&p_docnum=49&p_queryname=12 |title=Pulse's Space a New Odyssey for Chic|author=Mark K. Matthews |website=''The Orlando Sentinel'' |date=2004-07-09}}</ref><ref name=Hjelmgaard /><ref>{{cite magazine |url = http://www.motherjones.com/politics/2016/06/orlando-gay-nightclub-massacre-lgbt-community-history |title = Orlando's Pulse Nightclub Was Founded by a Woman Whose Brother Died from AIDS |first = James |last = West |date = 2016-06-12 |work = Mother Jones |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |issn = 0362-8841 |publisher = Foundation for National Progress |archive-date = 2021-02-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227231259/https://www.motherjones.com/politics/2016/06/orlando-gay-nightclub-massacre-lgbt-community-history/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。波马的哥哥约翰于1991年罹患[[艾滋病|艾滋病]]死去，2016年2月一位营销部员工表示，波马给夜店起这个名字是想“让约翰的脉搏继续跳动”<ref name=wapo>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/06/13/more-than-just-another-gay-club-pulse-was-founded-in-her-brothers-memory-and-named-for-his-beating-heart/|title=Orlando’s club Pulse owes its name and spirit to ‘loving brother’ who died from AIDS|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-13|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025191646/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2016/06/13/more-than-just-another-gay-club-pulse-was-founded-in-her-brothers-memory-and-named-for-his-beating-heart/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="next-feb">{{cite news |title = The Pulse of Orlando |date = 2013-02-03 |page =  |work = Next |location =  |url = http://nextmagazinefl.com/central-florida/the-pulse-of-orlando |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160617092046/http://nextmagazinefl.com/central-florida/the-pulse-of-orlando |archivedate = 2016-06-17 }}</ref>。该店专注于当地人才<ref name="next-feb" />。波马为确保哥哥的回忆在网络上显眼，便将店子形容为“不只是一个同性恋俱乐部”<ref name=wapo />。夜店成立时，雷格勒是佛罗里达戏剧协会（{{lang|en|Florida Theatrical Association}}）主席，于2010年在{{le|伊欧拉湖边公园|Lake Eola Park}}创立了两间同性恋夜店，2011年动身前往巴尔的摩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/breaking-news/os-ron-legler-leaving-orlando-20140218-story.html|title=Ron Legler, 'champion' of downtown and the arts, leaving Orlando|first=Orlando|last=Sentinel|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-13|archive-date=2020-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509012033/https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/breaking-news/os-ron-legler-leaving-orlando-20140218-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》称脉冲是12年来第一间“宣传艾滋病预防、乳腺病和移民权利知识的社区枢纽，据报它曾与骄傲站起来、{{le|佛罗里达州平等组织|Equality Florida}}和斑马联盟等宣教团体有合作<ref name=wapo />。

2016年6月12日，29岁的[[奥马尔·马丁|奥马尔·马丁]]在一场大规模枪击案中杀死49人，弄伤53人。袭击是美国历史上由单个枪手引发的死伤最严重大规模枪击案<ref name="LATimes">{{cite news |url = http://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-orlando-nightclub-shooting-20160612-snap-story.html |title = Fifty dead in Orlando gay nightclub shooting, worst mass killing in U.S. history; gunman reportedly pledged allegiance to Islamic State |newspaper = Los Angeles Times |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |date = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160612095327/http://www.latimes.com/nation/nationnow/la-na-orlando-nightclub-shooting-20160612-snap-story.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="lyons20160612">{{cite web |url = http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jun/12/orlando-shooting-nightclub-pulse-gunman |title = Orlando Pulse club attack: gunman behind shooting that killed 49 'named as Omar Mateen' |last = Lyons |first = Kate |date = 2016-06-12 |website = The Guardian |access-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160612100242/http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jun/12/orlando-shooting-nightclub-pulse-gunman |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="cbc">{{cite news |url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/florida-pulse-nightclub-shooting-1.3631419 |title = Gunman in nightclub shooting had been investigated for terrorist links |publisher = CBC News |date = 2016-06-12 |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2020-11-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108141637/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/florida-pulse-nightclub-shooting-1.3631419 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first = Lois |last = Beckett |url = http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jun/12/orlando-nightclub-deadliest-mass-shooting-terrorism |title = Orlando nightclub attack is deadliest US mass shooting in modern history |work = The Guardian |date = 2016-06-12 |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160612204653/http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2016/jun/12/orlando-nightclub-deadliest-mass-shooting-terrorism |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/orlando-nightclub-shooting-20-dead-terror-attack-at-florida-lgbt-club-gay-killed-explosion-bomb-a7077831.html |last = Yeung |first = Peter |title = Gunman's 'terror attack' on gay nightclub leaves 50 dead |date = 2016-06-12 |website = The Independent |language = en-GB |access-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160612130352/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/orlando-nightclub-shooting-20-dead-terror-attack-at-florida-lgbt-club-gay-killed-explosion-bomb-a7077831.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>，也是美国反同性恋历史上最严重的暴力事件<ref>{{cite web |first = Mark Joseph |last = Stern |url = http://www.slate.com/blogs/outward/2016/06/12/pulse_nightclub_shooting_and_tragic_history_of_violence_at_lgbtq_clubs_in.html |title = The Long, Tragic History of Violence at LGBTQ Bars and Clubs in America |work = Slate |date = 2016-06-12 |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2016-06-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160612172215/http://www.slate.com/blogs/outward/2016/06/12/pulse_nightclub_shooting_and_tragic_history_of_violence_at_lgbtq_clubs_in.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>和[[九一一恐怖袭击|九一一恐怖袭击]]以来美国本土最致命的恐怖袭击<ref name="cnn">{{cite news |url = http://www.cnn.com/2016/06/12/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting/index.html |title = 50 killed in Florida nightclub, shooter pledged ISIS allegiance |first1 = Ashley |last1 = Fantz |first2 = Faith |last2 = Karimi |first3 = Eliott C. |last3 = McLaughlin |publisher = CNN |date = 2016-06-12 |accessdate = 2016-06-12 |archive-date = 2019-05-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190525135958/https://www.cnn.com/2016/06/12/us/orlando-nightclub-shooting/index.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://news.sky.com/story/1710904/obama-orlando-an-act-of-terror-and-hate |title = Obama: Orlando An Act 